id: hac-96i2
title: Align typed WebSocket target discovery with current Home Assistant
description: "Correct target extraction field handling and add typed trigger and condition discovery alongside services, while retaining the generic WebSocket passthrough for the full dynamic API."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[4]: agent-discovery,home-assistant,targeting,websocket
created_at: "2026-07-21T18:59:08.180Z"
